@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hiwpcz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 - (tmp / (v1 + 0.83 - tmp + 0.71)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.59)) + 0.48)
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.95 * v1 + 0.20)) / v2)
    v2 = wp.sin((0.53 * v1))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.21 * v2))
    data[tid] = v0
